<p><a name="Google Search Interest"></a></p>
<h3 id="google-search-interest">Google Search Interest</h3>
<p>This figure tells us how many people in the US are searching for keywords such as ‚Äúhand sanitizer‚Äù or ‚Äúsympotom‚Äù. I suspect that as the community spread of the virus is being contained, we can expect to see a drop in searches for words like ‚Äúsympotom‚Äù and ‚Äúinfluenza‚Äù, similar to the trends shown in Singapore.</p>
